https://docs.python.org/3.6/library/tkinter.html#how-to-use-this-section
When trying to answer questions of the form “how do I do blah”, it is often best
to find out how to do “blah” in straight Tk, and then convert this back into the
corresponding tkinter call. Python programmers can often guess at the correct
Python command by looking at the Tk documentation. This means that in order to
use Tkinter, you will have to know a little bit about Tk.

